545
00:38:51,655 --> 00:38:55,284
- Oh, hello, dear.
- What's that, Cedric? Right! Coming.

546
00:38:55,910 --> 00:38:58,037
Mom, have you seen Shrek?

547
00:38:58,078 --> 00:39:00,915
I haven't.
You should ask your father.

548
00:39:01,081 --> 00:39:05,628
Be sure and use small words, dear.
He's a little slow this morning.

549
00:39:05,711 --> 00:39:08,130
- Can I help you, Your Majesty?
- Ah, yes!

550
00:39:09,264 --> 00:39:11,759
Exquisite.
What do you call this dish?

551
00:39:11,842 --> 00:39:14,970
