Your Majesty.

552
00:39:15,054 --> 00:39:18,807
Ah, yes. Very good then.
Carry on, Cedric.

553
00:39:18,891 --> 00:39:22,978
- Dad? Dad, have you seen Shrek?
- No, I haven't, dear.

554
