Coffee and a Monte Cristo. Now!

575
00:41:00,784 --> 00:41:03,996
Yes, Fairy Godmother.
Right away.

576
00:41:04,038 --> 00:41:06,832
Look, she's not seeing
any clients today, OK?

577
00:41:06,874 --> 00:41:09,084
That's OK, buddy.
We're from the union.

578
00:41:09,168 --> 00:41:10,127
The union?

579
00:41:10,210 --> 00:41:14,631
We represent the workers in all magical
industries, both evil and benign.

580
00:41:14,715 --> 00:41:16,425
Oh! Oh, right.

581
00:41:16,550 --> 00:41:19,595
Are you feeling at all
degraded or oppressed?

582
00:41:20,200 --> 00:41:23,349
A little.
We don't even have dental.

583
00:41:23,390 --> 00:41:25,100
They don't even have dental.

584
00:41:25,184 --> 00:41:27,519
Okay, we'll just have
a look around.

585
00:41:27,561 --> 00:41:28,771
Oh, by the way.

586
00:41:28,854 --> 00:41:32,191
I think it'd be better if the Fairy Godmother
didn't know we were here.

587
00:41:32,232 --> 00:41:34,276
Know what I'm saying? Huh?

588
00:41:35,444 --> 00:41:38,697
- Stop it.
- Of course. Go right in.

589
00:42:08,102 --> 00:42:09,812
A drop of desire.

590
00:42:10,896 --> 00:42:12,731
Naughty!

591
00:42:13,941 --> 00:42:15,567
A pinch of passion.

592
00:42:20,781 --> 00:42:23,158
And just a hint of...

593
00:42:23,784 --> 00:42:24,952
lust!

594
00:42:28,497 --> 00:42:30,457
Excuse me.

595
00:42:30,541 --> 00:42:32,251
Sorry to barge in like this...

596
00:42:32,292 --> 00:42:35,462
