the Little Mermaid, Pretty Woman...

608
00:43:12,791 --> 00:43:15,461
No, no, no, no, no!

609
00:43:15,502 --> 00:43:19,923
You see, ogres don't
live happily ever after.

610
00:43:20,007 --> 00:43:21,633
All right, look, lady!

611
00:43:21,675 --> 00:43:25,387
Don't you point
those dirty green sausages at me!

612
00:43:26,847 --> 00:43:28,599
Your Monte Cristo and coffee.

613
00:43:28,682 --> 00:43:30,184
Oh! Sorry.

614
00:43:30,267 --> 00:43:32,311
Ah, that's okay.

615
00:43:32,394 --> 00:43:34,688
We were just leaving.

616
00:43:34,771 --> 00:43:37,441
Very sorry to have wasted your time,
Miss Godmother.

617
00:43:37,524 --> 00:43:39,318
Just go.

618
00:43:39,359 --> 00:43:40,694
Come on, guys.

619
