a basket of roses.

624
00:44:24,238 --> 00:44:28,825
- Well, one of these has got to help.
- I was just concocting this very plan!

625
00:44:28,909 --> 00:44:31,995
Already our minds are becoming one.

626
00:44:32,496 --> 00:44:36,959
If we need an expert on licking
ourselves, we'll give you a call.

627
00:44:37,042 --> 00:44:38,669
