In some cultures, donkeys are revered
as the wisest of creatures.

646
00:45:32,639 --> 00:45:34,182
Especially us talking ones.

647
00:45:34,266 --> 00:45:36,393
Donkey!

648
00:45:38,020 --> 00:45:39,938
That'll have to do.
We've got company.

649
00:45:47,404 --> 00:45:48,697
Can we get on with this?

650
00:45:51,992 --> 00:45:53,619
Hurry!

651
00:46:02,210 --> 00:46:03,670
Nice catch, Donkey!

652
00:46:03,837 --> 00:46:05,756
Finally!
A good use for your mouth.

653
