Just get this place cleaned up!

667
00:47:17,744 --> 00:47:22,582
And somebody bring me something
deep fried and smothered in chocolate!

668
00:47:23,542 --> 00:47:27,045
- Mother!
- Charming. Sweetheart.

669
00:47:27,129 --> 00:47:30,590
This isn't a good time, pumpkin.
Mama's working.

670
00:47:30,674 --> 00:47:32,801
Whoa, what happened here?

671
00:47:32,884 --> 00:47:35,971
- The ogre, that's what!
- What? Where is he, Mom?

672
00:47:36,054 --> 00:47:38,557
I shall rend his head
from his shoulders!

673
00:47:38,640 --> 00:47:41,059
I will smite him where he stands!

674
00:47:41,101 --> 00:47:45,147
He will rue the very day he stole
my kingdom from me!

675
00:47:45,897 --> 00:47:49,735
Oh, put it away, Junior!
You're still going to be king.

676
00:47:49,776 --> 00:47:52,404
We'll just have to come up
with something smarter.

677
00:47:52,487 --> 00:47:54,531
Pardon...

678
00:47:54,614 --> 00:47:58,869
Everything is accounted for,
Fairy Godmother, except for one potion.

679
00:47:58,952 --> 00:47:59,995
What?

680
00:48:02,914 --> 00:48:06,126
I do believe we can make
this work to our advantage.

681
00:48:07,919 --> 00:48:11,631
Happily Ever After Potion.
Maximum strength.

682
00:48:11,715 --> 00:48:14,342
For you and your true love.

683
00:48:14,426 --> 00:48:17,095
If one of you drinks this,
you both will be fine.

684
00:48:17,179 --> 00:48:20,015
Happiness, comfort
and beauty divine.

685
00:48:20,098 --> 00:48:23,810
