701
00:49:18,949 --> 00:49:22,869
- Well, here's to us, Fiona.
- Shrek?

702
00:49:22,953 --> 00:49:26,665
- You drink that, there's no going back.
- I know.

703
00:49:26,706 --> 00:49:28,625
- No more wallowing in the mud?
- I know.

704
00:49:28,708 --> 00:49:30,377
- No more itchy butt crack?
- I know!

705
00:49:30,460 --> 00:49:32,838
- But you love being an ogre!
- I know!

706
00:49:36,591 --> 00:49:38,552
But I love Fiona more.

707
