at a first impression,

846
00:59:06,744 --> 00:59:09,163
but, well, what do you think?

847
00:59:13,418 --> 00:59:16,087
Fiona! Fiona!

848
00:59:17,755 --> 00:59:19,424
Fiona!

849
00:59:19,507 --> 00:59:22,990
- Fiona!
- Fiona, Fiona!

850
00:59:23,594 --> 00:59:27,098
Oh, shoot! I don't think they
can hear us, pigeon.

851
00:59:29,725 --> 00:59:33,104
Don't you think you've already
messed her life up enough?

852
00:59:33,980 --> 00:59:36,065
I just wanted her to be happy.

853
00:59:36,149 --> 00:59:38,443
And now she can be.

854
00:59:38,526 --> 00:59:40,528
Oh, sweetheart.

855
00:59:40,611 --> 00:59:44,449
